{"tid":1416740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"史丹福監獄實驗同黑警有異曲同工既地方，值得參考","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:46:33.000Z","uid":252840,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de8ed704a7cbb3f25e6c6e1708df9707769e2772","tid":1416740,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/98076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F98076&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ee5481e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/98076</a><br />\n<br />\n實驗内容講既野好長，我唔講自己入上面條link睇。<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係，以家班差佬被迫扮演示威者既對面，姐係邪惡殘暴政府個面，以當佢地愈做得多殘暴行為，佢地會愈入戲，愈認同自己既行為，亦都愈撑個政府，愈黎愈顛。<br />\n<br />\n我認同警察高層入面有黑警，特别元朗個d，但係話所有基層警察都係黑警就唔認同，d基層差佬係下面無權無勢想黑都無得黑啦。<br />\n<br />\n以家警隊基層比政府同警隊高官擺左上枱，被迫站係我地既對立面，我地應該要拎佢地明大部分既良心警察唔係我地針對既對象！！<br />\n<br />\n大家少屌幾句，對住佢地唱下聖詩念下佛經感化下佢地會唔會好d,或者針對性咁直接屌d高層，令佢地明基層警察唔係我地既對立。<br />\n<br />\n當警察基層都軟化，香港政府就無哂手段"},{"pid":"5b51ebf26b4cdee0dd8cee956a764fa00d92ff4c","tid":1416740,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:30:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"189706e6e164b9bf3548cf598b2e7c8ae4ab7b43","tid":1416740,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4051fdfb3a89af264f57842aff2369e93798fde9","tid":1416740,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2faf96fc44a6c6038c4384fad814d7fd4403d37b","tid":1416740,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96ea7568646b7d0c3130f946901220e9e9484552","tid":1416740,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"367439c9db0a43daa9112f11ddbc270370065e5e","tid":1416740,"uid":77416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci